{"title":"Save 20% on Cycling Gear During the REI Member Moment Sale","link":"https://bikerumor.com/save-20-on-cycling-gear-during-the-rei-member-moment-sale/","date":1710766800000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/REI_Co_op_ebike-800x567.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"567\" alt=\"(Photo/REI Co-op)\" /></p>\n<p><strong>The REI Member Moment Sale</strong> is your seasonal opportunity to save on bikes, shoes, or apparel — as well as get early access to exclusive items.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>During the Member Moment Sale, March 15–25, members can use the coupon code “MEMBER24” at checkout to save 20% on any new gear. That’s a great opportunity to save on new cycling equipment, whether it’s a big ticket item or a fresh pair of socks. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Members can save another 20% on one REI Outlet item during the event, too.  </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out the latest designs from popular cycling brands below for a glimpse of what’s on tap just in time for all of your spring rides, races, and spin-to-win fun! </p>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreimembermomq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fs%2Fnew-arrivals\" target=\"_blank\">Shop New Arrivals at REI</a>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreimembermomq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fs%2Fcycling-new-arrivals\" target=\"_blank\">Shop New Cycling Gear at REI</a>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Screen-Shot-2024-03-12-at-9.57.50-AM.png\"><img width=\"1516\" height=\"945\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Screen-Shot-2024-03-12-at-9.57.50-AM.png\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Screen-Shot-2024-03-12-at-9.57.50-AM.png 1516w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Screen-Shot-2024-03-12-at-9.57.50-AM-297x185.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Screen-Shot-2024-03-12-at-9.57.50-AM-800x499.png 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Screen-Shot-2024-03-12-at-9.57.50-AM-120x75.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Screen-Shot-2024-03-12-at-9.57.50-AM-768x479.png 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo/REI Co-op)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>REI Member Benefits</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition to this one-time discount, REI offers rewards to its loyal customers. As a member, you can take advantage of exclusive deals, get early access to limited-edition items, and receive expert advice from REI’s passionate outdoor enthusiasts. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ll also be supporting REI as it invests in eco-friendly initiatives, conservation projects, and communities that work to protect nature.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you’re not already a member, you can sign up now and enjoy the 20% Member Moment discount.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>New Cycling Gear</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreimembermomq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F219532%2Fshimano-ex3-cycling-shoes-mens\" target=\"_blank\">Shimano EX3 Cycling Shoes — Men’s</a>: $120</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Shimano-EX3-Cycling-Shoes-Mens.jpg\"><img width=\"2200\" height=\"1467\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Shimano-EX3-Cycling-Shoes-Mens.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Shimano-EX3-Cycling-Shoes-Mens.jpg 2200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Shimano-EX3-Cycling-Shoes-Mens-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Shimano-EX3-Cycling-Shoes-Mens-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Shimano-EX3-Cycling-Shoes-Mens-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Shimano-EX3-Cycling-Shoes-Mens-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Shimano-EX3-Cycling-Shoes-Mens-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Shimano-EX3-Cycling-Shoes-Mens-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Shimano-EX3-Cycling-Shoes-Mens-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Shimano’s EX3 Cycling Shoes have mesh uppers for airflow, a city-touring outsole, and SPD cleat placement in the midfoot for comfort during more casual rides. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Shimano designed these with walking in mind, too. There’s a wider forefoot to reduce cleat chattering and the EX midsoles have an EVA foam to absorb impacts while riding and cushion while walking. </p>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreimembermomq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F219532%2Fshimano-ex3-cycling-shoes-mens\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Men’s</a>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreimembermomq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F199864%2Fwild-rye-ramsey-mountain-bike-shorts-womens%3Fcolor%3DPOPPY-BLUEBIRD\" target=\"_blank\">Wild Rye Ramsey Mountain Bike Shorts — Women’s</a>: $57</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-Rye-Ramsey-Mountain-Bike-Shorts-W.jpg\"><img width=\"2200\" height=\"1358\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-Rye-Ramsey-Mountain-Bike-Shorts-W.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-Rye-Ramsey-Mountain-Bike-Shorts-W.jpg 2200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-Rye-Ramsey-Mountain-Bike-Shorts-W-297x183.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-Rye-Ramsey-Mountain-Bike-Shorts-W-800x494.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-Rye-Ramsey-Mountain-Bike-Shorts-W-120x74.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-Rye-Ramsey-Mountain-Bike-Shorts-W-768x474.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-Rye-Ramsey-Mountain-Bike-Shorts-W-1536x948.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-Rye-Ramsey-Mountain-Bike-Shorts-W-2048x1264.jpg 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Designed for women, the Wild Rye Ramsey has a 12-inch inseam to fit long and provide coverage. You’ll also get protection from the sun, thanks to the UPF 50 shield fabric. The shorts are light and breathable and have a simple zippered pocket. </p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreimembermomq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F199864%2Fwild-rye-ramsey-mountain-bike-shorts-womens%3Fcolor%3DPOPPY-BLUEBIRD\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Now</a>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreimembermomq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F229413%2Fpatagonia-dirt-craft-bike-shorts-20-mens\" target=\"_blank\">Patagonia Dirt Craft Bike Shorts 2.0 — Men’s</a>: $199</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Patagonia-Dirt-Craft-Bike-Shorts-2.0-Mens.jpg\"><img width=\"2200\" height=\"1467\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Patagonia-Dirt-Craft-Bike-Shorts-2.0-Mens.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Patagonia-Dirt-Craft-Bike-Shorts-2.0-Mens.jpg 2200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Patagonia-Dirt-Craft-Bike-Shorts-2.0-Mens-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Patagonia-Dirt-Craft-Bike-Shorts-2.0-Mens-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Patagonia-Dirt-Craft-Bike-Shorts-2.0-Mens-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Patagonia-Dirt-Craft-Bike-Shorts-2.0-Mens-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Patagonia-Dirt-Craft-Bike-Shorts-2.0-Mens-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Patagonia-Dirt-Craft-Bike-Shorts-2.0-Mens-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Patagonia-Dirt-Craft-Bike-Shorts-2.0-Mens-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Dirt Craft 2.0 updates Patagonia’s bike shorts with more eco-friendly fabrics, including stretchy nylon and polyester sourced from fishing nets and ocean plastics. The removable padded liner has contoured chamois and mesh panels to help with airflow and employs a few technologies to reduce odors and aid wicking. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>They fit low enough to touch kneepads and have an external waist adjustment to dial the fit as you ride. There are two front pockets and two secure-zip thigh pockets.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreimembermomq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F229413%2Fpatagonia-dirt-craft-bike-shorts-20-mens\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Now</a>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreimembermomq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F152974%2Fbontrager-dual-charger-floor-pump\" target=\"_blank\">Bontrager Dual Charger Floor Pump</a>: $75</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Bontrager-Dual-Charger-Floor-Pump.jpg\"><img width=\"2200\" height=\"1467\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Bontrager-Dual-Charger-Floor-Pump.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Bontrager-Dual-Charger-Floor-Pump.jpg 2200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Bontrager-Dual-Charger-Floor-Pump-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Bontrager-Dual-Charger-Floor-Pump-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Bontrager-Dual-Charger-Floor-Pump-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Bontrager-Dual-Charger-Floor-Pump-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Bontrager-Dual-Charger-Floor-Pump-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Bontrager-Dual-Charger-Floor-Pump-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Bontrager-Dual-Charger-Floor-Pump-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>A dual-purpose pump that can inflate tires with Presta and Schrader valves. The Bontrager Dual Charger floor pump has a 4-inch base with three legs to prevent wobbling while pumping. Its gauge is mounted to the base as is the lever to switch between high-volume and high-pressure settings.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreimembermomq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F152974%2Fbontrager-dual-charger-floor-pump\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Now</a>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreimembermomq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F216583%2Fsmith-engage-2-mips-bike-helmet\" target=\"_blank\">Smith Engage 2 MIPS</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreimembermomq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F216588%2Fsmith-persist-2-mips-bike-helmet\" target=\"_blank\">Persist 2 MIPS Bike Helmet</a>: $130</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Smith-Persist-2-Mips-and-Engage-2-Mips-Bike-Helmet.jpg\"><img width=\"2200\" height=\"1130\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Smith-Persist-2-Mips-and-Engage-2-Mips-Bike-Helmet.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Smith-Persist-2-Mips-and-Engage-2-Mips-Bike-Helmet.jpg 2200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Smith-Persist-2-Mips-and-Engage-2-Mips-Bike-Helmet-297x153.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Smith-Persist-2-Mips-and-Engage-2-Mips-Bike-Helmet-800x411.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Smith-Persist-2-Mips-and-Engage-2-Mips-Bike-Helmet-120x62.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Smith-Persist-2-Mips-and-Engage-2-Mips-Bike-Helmet-768x394.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Smith-Persist-2-Mips-and-Engage-2-Mips-Bike-Helmet-1536x789.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Smith-Persist-2-Mips-and-Engage-2-Mips-Bike-Helmet-2048x1052.jpg 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Smith Engage 2 MIPS bike helmet is updated with high-absorption Zonal Koroyd materials to add to its MIPS energy-dissipating impact protection. It’s also ventilated, with a dial-adjust fit, and lined with a single layer of webbing. It has 20 fixed vents for airflow and a two-position visor that rotates to stow eyewear. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Smith Persist 2 MIPS bike helmet is also updated to Zonal Koroyd materials and has a dial-adjustable fit. Smith also extended the helmet’s back coverage for a better, locked-in feel on your head. The Persist has 21 fixed vents and fits Smith eyewear in two of them. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreimembermomq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F216583%2Fsmith-engage-2-mips-bike-helmet\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Engage 2</a><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreimembermomq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F216588%2Fsmith-persist-2-mips-bike-helmet\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Persist 2</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreimembermomq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F182344%2Fgarmin-varia-rtl515-rearview-radar-taillight\" target=\"_blank\">Garmin Varia Radar Tail Light</a>: $200</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Garmin-Varia-RTL515-Rearview-Radar-Taillight-1.jpg\"><img width=\"2200\" height=\"1467\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Garmin-Varia-RTL515-Rearview-Radar-Taillight-1.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Garmin-Varia-RTL515-Rearview-Radar-Taillight-1.jpg 2200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Garmin-Varia-RTL515-Rearview-Radar-Taillight-1-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Garmin-Varia-RTL515-Rearview-Radar-Taillight-1-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Garmin-Varia-RTL515-Rearview-Radar-Taillight-1-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Garmin-Varia-RTL515-Rearview-Radar-Taillight-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Garmin-Varia-RTL515-Rearview-Radar-Taillight-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Garmin-Varia-RTL515-Rearview-Radar-Taillight-1-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Garmin-Varia-RTL515-Rearview-Radar-Taillight-1-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Big lighting in a slim package, the Varia RTL515 is also your lookout and can send alerts to a companion device so you know when vehicles are coming up behind you. The light pairs with the Garmin Edge bike computer and radar display unit, as well as compatible wearables. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Varia provides visibility up to 1 mile and can run in peloton mode, with intensity flashes. Battery life can last up to 16 hours in day flash mode and up to six hours in solid mode</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreimembermomq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F182344%2Fgarmin-varia-rtl515-rearview-radar-taillight\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Now</a>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreimembermomq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F226306%2Fthule-epos-2-bike-hitch-rack\" target=\"_blank\">Thule Epos 2-Bike Hitch Rack</a>: $1,000</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Thule-Epos-2-Bike-Hitch-Rack.jpg\"><img width=\"2200\" height=\"1467\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Thule-Epos-2-Bike-Hitch-Rack.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Thule-Epos-2-Bike-Hitch-Rack.jpg 2200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Thule-Epos-2-Bike-Hitch-Rack-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Thule-Epos-2-Bike-Hitch-Rack-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Thule-Epos-2-Bike-Hitch-Rack-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Thule-Epos-2-Bike-Hitch-Rack-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Thule-Epos-2-Bike-Hitch-Rack-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Thule-Epos-2-Bike-Hitch-Rack-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Thule-Epos-2-Bike-Hitch-Rack-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Made to fit all kinds of bikes, the Thule Epos 2-bike hitch rack uses a telescopic bike attachment system with pivoting cradles and reinforced straps to hold any part of a frame or wheel. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It has a load capacity of 75 lbs. per bike and a total of 140 lbs. There’s 9.8 inches of room between bike trays to reduce bike-on-bike bangs, and ratcheting buckles and straps to fasten in tires up to 3.2 inches wide. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The rack itself is fully foldable for convenient installation and storage. When mounted, you should still be able to access your trunk thanks to its outboard pedal tilt.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreimembermomq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F226306%2Fthule-epos-2-bike-hitch-rack\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Now</a>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://